ets it as about being best friends. Nami turns her anger towards Sora, slapping him to the floor and raping him. The two then reach to have consensual sex, with Nami ignoring Sora the next day on.\n}}\n}}\n\n==Reception==\nChris Beveridge commends the OVA for \"good character designs, some good eroticism\". He further comments, \"While we get a fair bit of upper body nudity, there\u2019s no genitalia involved for those that are looking for that aspect of it ... it\u2019s not hiding the sex, but it\u2019s also straddling the line in a way to try to appeal to more people while not going all hardcore.\"<ref name=\"Beveridge\">{{cite web|last=Beveridge |first=Chris |date=May 29, 2013 |url=http://www.fandompost.com/2013/05/29/aki-sora-hentai-anime-dvd-review/ |title=''Aki Sora'' Hentai Anime DVD Review|publisher=Famdom Post |accessdate=December 27, 2013 }}</ref>\n\n==See also==\n{{Portalbar|Anime and manga}}\n* [[A Wish of My Sister]] - previous hentai manga by the same author, which characters (Keisuke and his unnamed sister) are similar in appearance and actions with Sora and Aki\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{ann|manga|11149}}\n\n{{Hoods Entertainment}}\n{{Jukki Hanada}}\n\n[[Category:2008 manga]]\n[[Category:2009 anime OVAs]]\n[[Category:2010 anime OVAs]]\n[[Category:Akita Shoten manga]]\n[[Category:Anime Works]]\n[[Category:Hentai anime and manga]]\n[[Category:Hoods Entertainment]]\n[[Category:Incest in fiction]]\n[[Category:Sh\u014dnen manga]]\n", "name_user": "Pazio Paz", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eEpisode list", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aki_Sora"}
